{"tid":811990,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇粉俠傳]7大取材於香港動畫，攻殼機動隊竟非第一","createTime":"2018-09-09T09:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T01:33:59.000Z","uid":8307,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f641f1ab175ea82033bcf469c5a4aeb25499dd67","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"第七位：<br />\n百變小櫻劇場版　相約在香港<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/IziGd7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIziGd7V.jpg&h=b7fdfb9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8z8eTRK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8z8eTRK.jpg&h=200aebf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/K34ujyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK34ujyw.jpg&h=831c87a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深入民心動畫，忠實程現出香港風景。<br />\n於多年後續作clear card篇，女主角木資本櫻仍保留著在香港旅行所拍攝的相片。"},{"pid":"918ed2ba9050e81925a59f939bc14ad7726f88bb","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"第七位圖片來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6190606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6190606&d=SuDdN0eGUOeRjBjatkZNKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d9cf560e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6190606</a><br />\n<br />\n第六位：<br />\nJOJO奇妙冒險星塵鬥士篇<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/edeab4ab5b29a0acbf8b908f7bd37819/tumblr_inline_nv1hztQHCS1tbkv6k_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fedeab4ab5b29a0acbf8b908f7bd37819%2Ftumblr_inline_nv1hztQHCS1tbkv6k_1280.png&h=bf9f1b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背景設定於1987年，主角空條Ｑ太郎路途經過香港，與銀色戰車的替身使者波波於虎豹別墅展開激戰，場景相當經典。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/noT9fMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnoT9fMu.png&h=fbb2868f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Qt2cbmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQt2cbmz.jpg&h=27e71b97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24d0302c778912c6759420352b2f4e61983f8606","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"第五位：<br />\n機動武鬥傳G GUNDAM<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/175438_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F175438_0d5b1c4c7f720f698946c7f6ab08f687.jpg&h=c0845399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n動畫將香港八九十年代風格與科幻風格融合，更為刻意動畫編上粵語插曲<br />\n導演今川泰宏更是資深香港通和功夫片愛好者，、除了將『機動武鬥傳G高達』的舞台定為新香港並植入大量邵氏武俠和新派武俠片元素之外，還為日本德間書店出版的古龍小說日譯本撰寫過序言。"},{"pid":"edcc6bf1110dc32e9d640cd568059a4652bf6624","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"第四位：<br />\n軍火女王<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7SGTD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7SGTD.jpg&h=5bd9626d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信已經令大部份連登仔勃起，但劇情關於香港只有一小部份，所以大大扣分。"},{"pid":"160b19123e8e2a4f32e4de125345da738cabc71c","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"第三位：<br />\n星際牛仔cowboy bebop<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/b21HcSrrBu8pi/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fb21HcSrrBu8pi%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b0cd0449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大量向八九十年代港產片致敬畫面，從非物質文化融入故事之中<br />\n一個字 勁!"},{"pid":"d4a58b8feca65c86169ece7a887058188d84d006","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"第二位：<br />\n攻殻機動隊　押井守版<br />\n<img src=\"http://gifimage.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ghost-in-the-shell-1995-gif-11.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgifimage.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fghost-in-the-shell-1995-gif-11.gif&h=b970c43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/74UvDWsKpjhDi/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F74UvDWsKpjhDi%2Fsource.gif&h=caa4219f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xUA7bipNz3dwu59JqU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxUA7bipNz3dwu59JqU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=93e05014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《攻殼機動隊》是日本動畫史上的里程碑，也是押井守的代表作之一，<br />\n完美將香港街景與cyberpunk風格融合，作畫即是在現今亦是數一數二。"},{"pid":"04ccef637ed7bd924f8fd504cae10f3afebca128","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":31,"dislike":33,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"第一位：<br />\n進擊的巨人<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/19/Attack_on_Titan_profile.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20130529154913\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F19%2FAttack_on_Titan_profile.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130529154913&h=d75afe22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在當年推出動畫版時網上談論急升，有大量網民認為進擊的巨人劇情緊凑，甚至聯想到香港逐步被內地攻陷，以及香港人固步自封等中港矛盾問題。<br />\nTVB更在進擊的巨人宣傳片旁白暗諷香港現況： <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我們渴望自由　但不敢抗爭 <br />\n追求平等　卻又戀慕權力 <br />\n以前我們畏縮　今天更加妥協 <br />\n口口聲聲尋求公義　但卻自甘墮落 <br />\n將來　注定失去更多<br />\n</span><br />\n進擊的巨人第一位當之無愧<br />\n奇文共賞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4436502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4436502&d=SuDdN0eGUOeRjBjatkZNKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=01571ef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4436502</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4453799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4453799&d=SuDdN0eGUOeRjBjatkZNKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=13968bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4453799</a>"},{"pid":"444a573d42a39cc3baa46caae7139edfb33d7154","tid":811990,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"UBI 大革命=香港神作"},{"pid":"30839ad1191e32fc11080a04da59b27c6e268deb","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444a573d42a39cc3baa46caae7139edfb33d7154","tid":811990,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"UBI 大革命=香港神作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"你開返個取材於香港既電子遊戲"},{"pid":"99d300e1a8aca9664eab6410858c3fed20a971d8","tid":811990,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"巨人神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c6fac2cb2579c48bfad5e7ae30a2d9d9a3e967","tid":811990,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"樓主港毒狗?"},{"pid":"66893741d5d6a82753be838e6f3ba038b228c06a","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b9c6fac2cb2579c48bfad5e7ae30a2d9d9a3e967","tid":811990,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"樓主港毒狗?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"68e3e4c235d31a045c48049e3c8ddc03bf4a7dd7","tid":811990,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30839ad1191e32fc11080a04da59b27c6e268deb","tid":811990,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444a573d42a39cc3baa46caae7139edfb33d7154","tid":811990,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"UBI 大革命=香港神作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"你開返個取材於香港既電子遊戲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09